Job Title: Application Tester with PV /LSS domain

Key Responsibilities

Execute manual and automated test cases to validate application functionality and performance.
Develop, maintain, and review test plans, test cases, and test scripts.
Identify, document, and track software defects using appropriate tools.
Proficient in SQL with practical experience in writing complex queries for data validation and testing purposes.
Collaborate with developers, business analysts, and other stakeholders to understand requirements
Ensure compliance with GxP and other regulatory standards during the testing process.
Participate in the Testing and Quality (TQ) process and contribute to continuous improvement.

Qualifications

Minimum 7-8 years of experience in software application testing.
Knowledge on PV or LSS domain
Strong understanding of software testing methodologies and the TQ process.
Experience with GxP-compliant testing frameworks is highly preferred
